ccessing AdService.\n\n### JSON Output\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"rpc error\", \"failed to retrieve ads\", \"Exception\", \"java.lang.Error\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"Memory spike on node aiops-k8s-04 impacting multiple services' functionality.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Errors with retrieving ads recorded in logs, potentially linked to aiops-k8s-04 node's memory usage.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Java exceptions within adservice indicating service-level failure.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Consistent java.lang.Exception logs impacting adservice functionality, reflecting RPC errors in logs.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"RPC errors while interacting with adservice pointing towards communication issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Multiple logs across aiops-k8s-03, aiops-k8s-07, and aiops-k8s-04 nodes show 'failed to retrieve ads'.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nGiven these hypotheses, further investigation into node performance metrics and underlying application-level diagnostics for `adservice` should be considered critical for isolating the root cause."}
